File:ex1a.cc
Printing the difference of 3 numbers
===============================================================================
Writen by: Michael Shriki, id = 305599417, login = michaelshr

This program calculate the difference between 3 numbers and print the results

Compile: g++ -Wall ex1a.cc –oex1a
Run: ex1a
Input: 	3 numbers as you wish;
            e.g. 5 3 7.

Output: the difference between them.
	    e.g. 0 2 -2
		 -2 0 -4
		 2 4 0

===============================================================================

File:ex1b.cc
Calculate area and perimeter of a triangle
=========================================
Writen by: Michael Shriki, id = 305599417, login = michaelshr

This program calculate area of triangle

Compile: g++ -Wall ex1b.cc –oex1b
Run: ex1b
Input: 	The three sides of a triangle;
            e.g. 5 3 7 for the traingle: A = 5, B = 3, C = 7.

Output: The area and perimeter of the traingle.

